msgid "Minimize current window"
msgstr "最小化当前窗口"

msgid "Timed minimize / restore"
msgstr "最小化 / 恢复（限时恢复）"

msgid "Trigger custom shortcut"
msgstr "触发自定义快捷键"

msgid "Show desktop / restore"
msgstr "显示桌面 / 恢复"

msgid "Maximize / restore"
msgstr "最大化 / 还原"

msgid "Close current window"
msgstr "关闭当前窗口"

msgid "Always on top / restore"
msgstr "窗口置顶 / 还原"

msgid "Hide all normal windows"
msgstr "隐藏所有普通窗口"

msgid "Do nothing"
msgstr "不执行任何操作"

msgid "Set shortcut"
msgstr "设置快捷键"

msgid "Clear shortcut"
msgstr "清空快捷键"

msgid "Press a shortcut…"
msgstr "请按快捷键…"

msgid "Panel Actions"
msgstr "面板动作"

msgid "Triggering"
msgstr "触发说明"

msgid "Only empty areas of the top panel respond. Buttons, tray icons, the clock, and menus are ignored automatically."
msgstr "只有顶部面板的空白区域会响应，按钮、托盘图标、时钟和菜单区域会自动忽略。"

msgid "Gesture map"
msgstr "手势映射"

msgid "Left button uses double-click. Middle and right buttons use single-click."
msgstr "左键使用双击；中键和右键使用单击。"

msgid "Capture left single click"
msgstr "捕获左键单击"

msgid "Consume a single left click on empty panel space and do not let the panel default behavior run."
msgstr "在面板空白处单击左键时由扩展直接拦截，不再触发面板默认行为。"

msgid "Mouse actions"
msgstr "鼠标动作"

msgid "Each panel gesture can be bound to a different action, or multiple gestures can share the same action."
msgstr "三种鼠标手势可以分别绑定不同的窗口管理动作，也可以设置成相同动作。"

msgid "Left double-click"
msgstr "左键双击"

msgid "Default: Minimize current window"
msgstr "默认：最小化当前窗口"

msgid "Middle click"
msgstr "中键单击"

msgid "Default: Maximize / restore"
msgstr "默认：最大化 / 还原"

msgid "Right click"
msgstr "右键单击"

msgid "Default: Show desktop / restore"
msgstr "默认：显示桌面 / 恢复"

msgid "Timed restore window"
msgstr "最小化恢复时限"

msgid "Used by the timed minimize / restore action. Default is 2 seconds, adjustable from 1 to 10 seconds."
msgstr "用于“最小化 / 恢复（限时恢复）”，默认 2 秒，可设置 1 到 10 秒。"

msgid "Shortcut triggers"
msgstr "快捷键触发"

msgid "When a gesture is bound to \"Trigger custom shortcut\", it executes the shortcut recorded here for that specific mouse button."
msgstr "当某个鼠标手势绑定为“触发自定义快捷键”时，会执行这里为该手势单独录制的快捷键。"

msgid "Left double-click shortcut"
msgstr "左键双击快捷键"

msgid "For example, record Super+L to lock the screen when the left double-click gesture triggers a custom shortcut."
msgstr "例如录制 Super+L，用于左键双击绑定“触发自定义快捷键”时执行。"

msgid "Middle click shortcut"
msgstr "中键单击快捷键"

msgid "Executed when the middle click gesture is bound to trigger a custom shortcut."
msgstr "用于中键单击绑定“触发自定义快捷键”时执行。"

msgid "Right click shortcut"
msgstr "右键单击快捷键"

msgid "Executed when the right click gesture is bound to trigger a custom shortcut."
msgstr "用于右键单击绑定“触发自定义快捷键”时执行。"

msgid "Diagnostics"
msgstr "调试"

msgid "Useful when checking blank-area hit detection, actor paths, and action dispatch."
msgstr "用于排查空白区域命中、actor 路径和动作分发情况。"

msgid "Enable debug logging"
msgstr "启用调试日志"

msgid "Write click hit-testing and action dispatch information to the GNOME Shell log."
msgstr "把点击命中和动作分发信息写入 GNOME Shell 日志。"
